Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:10.06,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hear ye! Hear ye!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.06,0:00:14.95,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,The Ponyville Foal and Filly Fair is almost ready to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:28.41,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Just because the attendees are young
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.41,0:00:31.59,Rarity,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean they don't deserve my very best creative work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.75,0:00:36.34,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Why, this puppet theatre is going to be the talk of the Foal and Filly Fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:40.31,Spike,,0,0,0,,How could it not be? You're the one making it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.59,0:00:46.50,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't have made it without the help of one of my dearest and most supportive friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.50,0:00:49.40,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You are my favorite dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:51.54,Spike,,0,0,0,,Your favourite dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:53.02,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh gee.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.02,0:00:57.09,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The hours have been long, the work taxing beyond compare.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:01.15,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But it'll all be worth it when we hear these three little words…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:03.36,Spike,,0,0,0,,This is awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.36,0:01:04.42,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Awful?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.42,0:01:07.00,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And completely unusable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:12.30,Somepony,,0,0,0,,It doesn't travel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:16.06,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And no room for my puppets!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:21.54,Somepony,,0,0,0,,It appears I won't have a travelling puppet theater to use after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:28.12,Spike,,0,0,0,,I don't know what that guy was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:30.94,Spike,,0,0,0,,This thing is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:16.13,Rarity,,0,0,0,,This is terrible! Simply terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:24.58,Spike,,0,0,0,,So that puppeteer didn't like your exquisitely crafted best puppet theater in a history of puppeteers and puppet theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:28.58,Spike,,0,0,0,,You can just contribute something else to the Foal and Filly Fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:32.22,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I suppose I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:34.45,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Forget it, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:37.67,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'll never have something finished in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:48.11,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I wanted to leave my creative mark on the fair, and I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:51.27,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Miserably.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:55.82,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And that makes me miserable!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:08.94,Spike,,0,0,0,,There's gotta be something in here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:12.42,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's not who, it's what!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:15.89,Spike,,0,0,0,,Like what can help Rarity make something in time for the fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.89,0:03:19.56,Spike,,0,0,0,,She really really really wants to make a creative contribution!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:21.65,Spike,,0,0,0,,She said I'm her favorite dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:24.88,Spike,,0,0,0,,So it's up to me to come through for her in her time of need!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:30.27,Spike,,0,0,0,,There's gotta be some kind of spell that'll do the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:33.85,Spike,,0,0,0,,Come on, help the dragon out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:45.54,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's not for me, it's for Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:48.45,Spike,,0,0,0,,The one who made you that bowtie you like so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:51.96,Spike,,0,0,0,,Okay, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.62,Spike,,0,0,0,,You don't think we should use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:03.88,Spike,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:31.62,Spike,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:34.62,Spike,,0,0,0,,If I wasn't supposed to have it, it wouldn't be so easy to get!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:37.73,Spike,,0,0,0,,And it's covered in spikes! Like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:47.57,Spike,,0,0,0,,Inspiration manifestation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:50.36,Spike,,0,0,0,,Instantly brings ideas to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:53.29,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm liking the looks of this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:09.41,Spike,,0,0,0,,Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:11.46,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Leave me be!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:16.70,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Can't you see how distraught, disappointed and downtrodden I still am?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:19.14,Spike,,0,0,0,,But I brought you something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:22.51,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Unless it's another carton of vanilla oat swirl
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:25.15,Rarity,,0,0,0,,or word that the festival has been cancelled,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:27.85,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'm interested!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:30.22,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:34.47,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Spike, precious scales, I already have magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:40.39,Spike,,0,0,0,,But not the kind that helps you create something in time for the fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:41.89,Spike,,0,0,0,,This can!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:45.74,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I suppose it's worth a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:50.85,Rarity,,0,0,0,,From in the head to out in the world\NEvery thought to action
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:56.47,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Hold close this book, and through its spell\NYou'll start a chain reaction
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:05:59.79,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Projecting forth whatever beauty you see
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:05.30,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Only when true words are spoken\NWill you finally be set free
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:06.47,Spike,,0,0,0,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:09.52,Rarity,,0,0,0,, There's only one way to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:19.39,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh my! I thought about making this a much more beautiful spellbook
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:21.09,Rarity,,0,0,0,,and I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:27.74,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Dear, dear, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:29.25,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Here I was about to give up,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:33.12,Rarity,,0,0,0,,but like a true friend you've come through with flying colors!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:37.57,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Come! We must find the puppeteer right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.57,0:06:41.77,Rarity,,0,0,0,,So that I may provide him with the most fabulous theater he has ever imagined!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:42.92,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Or
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:47.02,Rarity,,0,0,0,,should I say, that I've ever imagined?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:07:01.25,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Aha, Miss Rarity, come to see the show, I presume.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:08.19,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You notice I had to make do out of your recent failure to produce a functioning theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:19.15,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I think you'll find the new one I've created will be much more to your liking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:27.82,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Well, it is gorgeous,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:30.63,Somepony,,0,0,0,,but that was ever the problem, now, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:35.85,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Oh well, this one does seem to travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:41.33,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Plenty of room for my puppets!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:45.94,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I'd say, Miss Rarity, I don't know how you managed to do so in such a short amount of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:49.38,Somepony,,0,0,0,,but you seem to have redeemed yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:53.31,Somepony,,0,0,0,,How did you manage to do so in such a short time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:55.57,Spike,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, she used a sp…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:57.93,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Proper designer never reveals her tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:07.74,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Thank you again, Spike, for being such a dear friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:09.80,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And finding this book for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:11.71,Spike,,0,0,0,,My pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:14.14,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I can return it, now that the fair is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:15.30,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:18.20,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I've made my creative contribution as I'd hoped to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:19.51,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And all is well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:28.60,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Then again, perhaps I should keep it but a skotch longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.60,0:08:30.16,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You don't mind, do you, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:32.36,Spike,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.51,Spike,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:38.82,Spike,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:40.49,Spike,,0,0,0,,She'll keep it for a few more hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:41.62,Spike,,0,0,0,,No harm in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:52.64,Spike,,0,0,0,,Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:08:58.80,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:00.39,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:06.65,Spike,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:11.82,Spike,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:13.65,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've never been better!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.90,Rarity,,0,0,0,,This book you've given me is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:20.34,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Why, I've been up all night just creating and creating and creating and creating!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:24.45,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I have completed my fall line… for the next fifteen seasons!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:25.55,Spike,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:28.31,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But then I started thinking, why stop there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:32.72,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spike. I've always thought this town of ours could use a few beautifying upgrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:36.24,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And with this book I can make that happen with such ease!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.52,0:09:40.76,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You will support me in this endeavour by letting me keep this book just a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.59,Spike,,0,0,0,,Of course I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:55.28,Spike,,0,0,0,,What do you say we get a little breakfast before we get started?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:56.52,Rarity,,0,0,0,,No time for breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.52,0:09:58.52,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I want to get started right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:09:59.68,Spike,,0,0,0,,Technically…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:03.66,Spike,,0,0,0,,we do have time, because with that book held close you can just make things…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:06.47,Spike,,0,0,0,,Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:12.92,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Now, this is exactly what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:15.98,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Why, that cart hasn't an ounce of a stylish flair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:27.77,Granny Smith,,0,0,0,,My eyes playing tricks on me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:30.12,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What in rhubarb pie just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:34.00,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Isn't it gorgeous?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:35.22,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.22,0:10:39.27,Spike,,0,0,0,,You should ask Applejack if she wants you to get all the Apple family carts a makeover.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.27,0:10:39.94,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:42.83,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I don't really think I need to ask permission, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:44.93,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Everyone loves surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:47.46,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Especially when they are gorgeous ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:48.32,Spike,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:50.39,Spike,,0,0,0,,Everypony does love surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:56.53,Rarity,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't even tell anypony that it's me who's behind all the fabulous changes I'll be making.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:11:00.68,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Why, that'd be a fun little secret for the three of us to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:04.10,Spike,,0,0,0,,The… three… of us…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:06.72,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You, me…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:08.27,Rarity,,0,0,0,,and the book of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:13.19,Rarity,,0,0,0,,My marvelous, marvelous book.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.03,Spike,,0,0,0,,Of course…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:19.30,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Promise me you won't say a word to anypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:21.57,Spike,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:24.49,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I knew I could count on you, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:27.37,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And I also know just what I want to do next!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:30.06,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:31.45,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:35.57,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What in the…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:36.48,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Get…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:37.50,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,it…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:38.64,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,off…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:39.97,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:44.16,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I've always thought Rainbow Dash could use a little more glamour.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:45.35,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And now look at her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.50,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Cloud-busting with style!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:49.89,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Moving on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:52.49,Spike,,0,0,0,,She will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:53.76,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's just a dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:56.46,Spike,,0,0,0,,Wait for your favorite dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:07.55,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,La la-la la-la la-la la la…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:10.18,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,There you go, mister Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:16.00,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Don't you look so content in your little house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.51,0:12:18.05,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, my goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:21.00,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You're lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.23,0:12:23.28,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,No, not that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:25.04,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,That looks like that's a door to a…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:26.21,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:27.54,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Try that one over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:30.50,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,No, no. That is to a…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.66,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Shoe closet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:33.62,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:35.20,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Maybe try the staircase?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:38.08,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no. The other staircase.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:39.76,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Isn't it gorgeous?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:42.93,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's probably the most beautiful birdhouse ever created.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:43.89,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:46.90,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm just not sure how the bird feels about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:51.47,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What does a bird know about architectural design?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:53.17,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What matters is what you think, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:55.38,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And you love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:57.27,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:58.46,Spike,,0,0,0,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:12:59.67,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's so…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:02.18,Spike,,0,0,0,,Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:03.68,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:22.73,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.73,0:13:25.91,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But it could use a touch of class? Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:27.04,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:28.20,Spike,,0,0,0,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:43.72,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But this party doesn't even seem have a proper theme!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.72,0:13:46.69,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Let's do something about that. Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:49.33,Spike,,0,0,0,,You've already make things look really really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:51.84,Spike,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should stop while you're ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:53.45,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You are right, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:55.76,Rarity,,0,0,0,,There's so much to do elsewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:57.07,Spike,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:58.40,Spike,,0,0,0,,Elsewhere…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:00.84,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Just one more little thing before we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:08.90,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Why, this party is certain to make a society page now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:11.76,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Won't Pinkie Pie be pleased?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:14.43,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Happy, happy day to…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:15.20,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:21.54,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I am simply buzzing with ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:22.75,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Simply buzzing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:25.85,Spike,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:26.61,Spike,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:28.62,Spike,,0,0,0,,You've been at this for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:30.04,Spike,,0,0,0,,Haven't you take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.04,0:14:32.23,Spike,,0,0,0,,Give that brilliant mind of yours a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:33.60,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.51,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna stop now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:40.49,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Why, I won't stop until the every inch of Ponyville is benefited from my creative vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:45.69,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Starting with you, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:54.91,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You! Look! Fabulous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:57.32,Spike,,0,0,0,,All because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:15:02.17,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Anything for my favorite dragon and most supportive friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:02.93,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:04.93,Rarity,,0,0,0,,There's so much more to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:12.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Not you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:15.40,Spike,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, not me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:18.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, judging by that outfit, I thought for sure…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:19.29,Spike,,0,0,0,,What, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:21.56,Spike,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to try out a new look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:24.07,Spike,,0,0,0,,You like?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:29.41,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, in that case, have you seen anypony suspicious around?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:30.64,Spike,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:38.16,Mayor,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight, the gazebo has been turned into solid crystal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:41.48,Mayor,,0,0,0,,And two ponies are now trapped inside its walls!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:52.09,Spike,,0,0,0,,No! I made a promise to Rarity to keep this to myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:56.18,Spike,,0,0,0,,But you're right, Owlowiscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:57.72,Spike,,0,0,0,,I have to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.27,Spike,,0,0,0,,And once I do,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:03.23,Spike,,0,0,0,,I can forget Rarity thinking of me as the most supportive friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:07.69,Spike,,0,0,0,,I can forget Rarity thinking of me as a friend at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:19.15,Spike,,0,0,0,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:23.02,Spike,,0,0,0,,I promised I'll keep all of it between the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:27.86,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Of course it's weird that she meant me, her and the spellbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:30.11,Spike,,0,0,0,,But… The spellbook!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:31.30,Spike,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:36.08,Spike,,0,0,0,,If I didn't get it away from her, I bet she won't be able to use its magic anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:39.10,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh come on, it's the perfect plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:41.95,Spike,,0,0,0,,I just have to figure out which way she went.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:43.69,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:51.82,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking she's headed this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:09.80,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.29,0:17:13.00,Spike,,0,0,0,,Me? I was just…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:15.74,Spike,,0,0,0,,basking in your creative radiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:17.47,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:20.56,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You do say the nicest things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:21.66,Spike,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:24.16,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well, where was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:28.48,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:31.81,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Gold-plated rooftops for everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:41.04,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:47.26,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I have just had the most marvellous idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:52.20,Spike,,0,0,0,,Of course you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:53.44,Spike,,0,0,0,,You're Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:57.08,Rarity,,0,0,0,,My work here in Ponyville is nearly complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:18:02.55,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's time the rest of Equestria benefited from my creative vision?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:03.84,Spike,,0,0,0,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:07.80,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh! I'm thinking we go by chariot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:11.19,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Or, as everyone will soon be calling them, rariot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:16.65,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. We should definitely go by…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:22.99,Spike,,0,0,0,,How… how did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:25.04,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Why, whatever do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:28.86,Spike,,0,0,0,,The book. It's… I mean… You don't…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.86,0:18:30.16,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:31.42,Spike,,0,0,0,,The book is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:32.33,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:35.28,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Why it's right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:37.32,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I need my book, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:39.54,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What have you done with my book?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:43.00,Spike,,0,0,0,,Why would I do anyhting with your book.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:44.36,Spike,,0,0,0,,We're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:47.48,Spike,,0,0,0,,It was probably the owl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:51.18,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:53.83,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I don't seem to need it anymore, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:56.03,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:59.79,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I can feel its magic flowing within me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:03.28,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited! I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:05.02,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.02,0:19:06.99,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, the places we'll go, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:10.72,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Manehattan! Fillydelphia! Canterlot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:12.56,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And there you'll be by my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:14.44,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Just as you always have been here in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:18.65,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Your constant praise and adoration driving me to even greater heights!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:23.25,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Until there isn't an inch of Equestria that hasn't been utterly transformed by my
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:25.88,Rarity,,0,0,0,,creative genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:32.69,Spike,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:35.12,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:36.72,Spike,,0,0,0,,I said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:39.85,Spike,,0,0,0,,You've been changing things, but you haven't been making them better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:42.03,Spike,,0,0,0,,I should've told you the truth at the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:46.01,Spike,,0,0,0,,But I didn't, because I was trying to be a supportive friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.01,0:19:50.18,Spike,,0,0,0,,But instead I let you become something awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:52.50,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Awful?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:05.35,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.71,0:20:08.33,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Rarity? You're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:10.83,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:16.75,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Though by the looks of it, something quite terrifying has happened to Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.72,0:20:19.23,Spike,,0,0,0,,You happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:20.32,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:24.46,Spike,,0,0,0,,The last part of the spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.46,0:20:30.04,Rarity,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only when true words are spoken{\i0}\N{\i1}Will you finally be set free{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:34.73,Spike,,0,0,0,,The spell took over you and you wanted to change everything in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:37.71,Spike,,0,0,0,,I was afraid to tell you how I really felt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:41.20,Spike,,0,0,0,,But then I… I told you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:42.85,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Dearest Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:45.29,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You should never be afraid to tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:47.80,Rarity,,0,0,0,,We're friends, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.49,0:20:54.04,Spike,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today I learned how important it is to be honest with your friends{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:56.97,Spike,,0,0,0,,{\i1}when they're doing something that you don't think is right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.97,0:21:01.44,Spike,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A true friend knows that you're speaking up because you care about them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:02.67,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:05.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Never-ever-ever-ever
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:09.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,take another book out of the library at the castle without asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:14.42,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadence and Princess Luna have much better things to do than help me clean up Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:20.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how hard it was to reverse that much dark magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:24.41,Spike,,0,0,0,,You don't look so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:25.77,Spike,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.77,0:21:27.13,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm just being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:29.23,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's what good friends do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.21,0:21:36.15,Somepony,,0,0,0,,СЧАСТЛИВЫЙ ПОНЕЦ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.15,0:21:39.86,Somepony,,0,0,0,,anon2anon\Nsunnysubs.com
